1
00:00:00,970 --> 00:00:03,680
(Episode 50)

2
00:00:06,480 --> 00:00:07,480
Ma Seo Rin!

3
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:11,880
Shit.

4
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:12,880
Oh Jang Mi.

5
00:00:13,650 --> 00:00:16,620
Here comes the nag to chew me out
for being late.

6
00:00:17,560 --> 00:00:19,820
How does she feel so familiar
when we've only met a few times?

7
00:00:21,030 --> 00:00:22,490
Is this what family feels like?

8
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,030
No!

9
00:01:16,650 --> 00:01:18,350
Ma Seo Rin!

10
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,430
What happened?

11
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:34,330
Someone else jumped in.

12
00:01:36,170 --> 00:01:37,700
We took care of Oh Jang Mi, so we're good.

13
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,410
Let's go.

14
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,750
Ok Hee and Tok Hee...

15
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,550
Ok Hee and Tok Hee...

16
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,550
Mom, what's wrong?

17
00:01:56,090 --> 00:01:57,120
What's going on?

18
00:01:57,760 --> 00:02:00,660
Is Mom having another episode?
Should we take her to the hospital?

19
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:03,260
Mom, what's going on?

20
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:06,500
My Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

21
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,970
What in the world does that mean?

22
00:02:08,970 --> 00:02:10,800
Are you looking for the bunny?
It's right here.

23
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:12,470
No.

24
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:14,510
- No way!
- Mom!

25
00:02:14,570 --> 00:02:15,570
- Mom!
- Mom.

26
00:02:16,570 --> 00:02:17,610
No!

27
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,140
Mom.

28
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,360
Seo Rin.

29
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:39,730
Seo Rin.

30
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:54,610
Seo Rin...

31
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,800
Ma'am, are you conscious?

32
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,030
Are you okay?

33
00:03:14,330 --> 00:03:15,730
Ma'am, can you hear me?

34
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:18,700
Ma'am!

35
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:24,010
(Lawyer Kang Baek Ho)

36
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,550
I've just seen a whole new
side to Jang Mi.

37
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:31,080
There's never a dull moment with her.

38
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:35,750
She has so many ways of getting angry.
How am I supposed to make it up to her?

39
00:03:40,690 --> 00:03:43,330
I guess your mother isn't here.

40
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:46,360
Right. Are you looking for Lawyer Han?

41
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,030
She seems to have just stepped out.
Should I get her for you?

42
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:53,170
That's okay. It's lunchtime,
so I was hoping to have lunch with her.

43
00:03:53,370 --> 00:03:54,710
I brought some kimbap.

44
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:58,140
Since she's not here, I guess
I'll just have to eat with you, Baek Ho.

45
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,080
I've already eaten.

46
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,520
No, you haven't.

47
00:04:10,490 --> 00:04:13,390
- Here you go. Try this.
- Hey, what are you doing?

48
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:16,260
Please finish your business with Ms. Han
and be on your way.

49
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:20,630
Come on, just try this one.
I put in so much effort.

50
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:21,970
The kimbap is innocent, isn't it?

51
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:23,370
This is a law office.

52
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:26,370
It's not a place for people to just bring
in food and stink up the office.

53
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:29,640
It smells, so please get it out of here.

54
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:37,350
Unbelievable,
talk about putting up a wall.

55
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:44,260
So, Kang Baek Ho,
you only have eyes for Oh Jang Mi?

56
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:49,390
Just you wait.
I'll make you mine, no matter what.

57
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:53,130
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

58
00:04:55,270 --> 00:04:56,470
What's going on?

59
00:04:57,370 --> 00:04:59,040
Did they even do the job right?

60
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,840
Why is it taking so long?

61
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:08,910
Ma'am.

62
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:10,350
What?

63
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:14,650
Is something the matter?

64
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,590
Sorry. My mind was elsewhere.

65
00:05:22,490 --> 00:05:23,490
Here.

66
00:05:25,030 --> 00:05:26,030
Thanks.

67
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:36,640
What is Manager Lee doing?
I'm going out of my mind worrying.

68
00:05:42,010 --> 00:05:43,610
Now why is she calling?

69
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:49,820
- What's up?
- I said to add more garlic.

70
00:05:50,660 --> 00:05:52,090
CEO Chae.

71
00:05:52,890 --> 00:05:54,490
Listen, about Seo Rin...

72
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:58,730
I was keeping a close eye on her,
just like you ordered.

73
00:05:58,930 --> 00:06:01,170
What's with the long preamble?
Just spit it out.

74
00:06:01,570 --> 00:06:04,240
Don't tell me my Seo Rin isn't home.

75
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:09,070
About when she left...

76
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:10,980
What? She left?

77
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:13,710
What exactly do you do around the house?

78
00:06:14,110 --> 00:06:17,150
I told you to watch Seo Rin
and ensure she didn't leave!

79
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:18,720
Couldn't you do that?

80
00:06:21,890 --> 00:06:22,920
When did she leave?

81
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:26,420
She made it look like she was there
and then she just took off.

82
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,360
How was I supposed to figure that out?

83
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:32,830
So you're telling me you don't even know
what time she left?

84
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:36,000
- That's right. I don't know, okay?
- What's with the attitude?

85
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:37,970
What, is Seo Rin your pet dog?

86
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:40,740
Do you want me
to keep her on a leash for you?

87
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:41,810
Shut up!

88
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:46,510
Why would she go as far as staging it
to look like she was asleep...

89
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:47,580
and then sneak out?

90
00:06:48,210 --> 00:06:51,420
Don't tell me she went to see Oh Jang Mi.

91
00:06:57,790 --> 00:06:58,890
Please, pick up.

92
00:06:59,690 --> 00:07:00,760
Come on, pick up.

93
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,400
How did it go?

94
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,370
Ma'am.

95
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:09,530
It's just...

96
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:24,650
(Emergency Room)

97
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:35,160
She's bleeding heavily. Check her pulse
and vitals, then get a neuro scan.

98
00:07:35,790 --> 00:07:38,660
We have two female victims,
late 20s to early 30s.

99
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,000
From the same accident.
One is in critical condition,

100
00:07:41,030 --> 00:07:42,270
and the other has minor injuries.

101
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:45,170
I found a wallet. Her name is Ma Seo Rin.

102
00:07:48,110 --> 00:07:49,410
(Paramedics)

103
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:54,350
Put her name down as Oh Jang Mi.

104
00:07:54,350 --> 00:07:56,610
I'll try calling a contact from her phone.

105
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:07,990
Chairman, something terrible has happened.

106
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,030
Director Ma...

107
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,030
was in a car accident.

108
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:15,030
What?

109
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,400
Oh my gosh, what did you say happened?

110
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,500
Seo Rin was in a car accident?

111
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,310
(Emergency Room)

112
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,550
(Oh Jang Mi)

113
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,270
(Ma Seo Rin)

114
00:08:54,710 --> 00:08:55,740
You were supposed to be at home!

115
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,810
Why did you sneak out
and end up like this?

116
00:08:58,540 --> 00:09:01,750
Seo Rin, it's Mom.
Please open your eyes. Come on.

117
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:10,760
(Bomdama)

118
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,660
(Jang Mi)

119
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:19,630
Oh Jang Mi, you went out again?
Where are you? Why aren't you answering...

120
00:09:21,130 --> 00:09:22,130
I'm sorry?

121
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:27,310
What did you say?
Jang Mi was in a car accident?

122
00:09:28,370 --> 00:09:29,970
(Emergency Medical Center)

123
00:09:30,210 --> 00:09:32,580
Where's Oh Jang Mi?
She was brought in after a car accident.

124
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,710
- Are you her family?
- Yes.

125
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,480
Please confirm this is hers.

126
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:40,450
It's Jang Mi's phone.

127
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:43,820
How badly is she hurt?
Is she going to be okay?

128
00:09:43,890 --> 00:09:47,560
She's lost a lot of blood.
The doctor will give you the details.

129
00:09:48,660 --> 00:09:49,760
What do we do?

130
00:10:07,450 --> 00:10:08,450
Jang Mi.

131
00:10:09,350 --> 00:10:11,350
I'm so sorry. It's all my fault.

132
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,050
I can't believe this.
What happened to you?

133
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:17,220
It hasn't even been that long
since Dad died,

134
00:10:17,490 --> 00:10:20,120
and now you're in an accident,
ending up like this?

135
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,130
Jang Mi, you can't be lying here
hurt like this.

136
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,560
Please.

137
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:32,440
Please, my sister has to make it.
How badly is she hurt? Tell me.

138
00:10:32,970 --> 00:10:33,970
Wait a minute.

139
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:36,570
Could this girl be...

140
00:10:38,010 --> 00:10:39,110
Oh Jang Mi?

141
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,280
What's gotten into you?

142
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,920
Just listen to your mother.

143
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:57,130
My sweet Seo Rin. This is your lucky mole.

144
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,300
Let me put it on for you.

145
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:14,050
She's just like my Seo Rin in every way.

146
00:11:14,810 --> 00:11:16,680
Except she doesn't have the mole
behind her ear.

147
00:11:47,310 --> 00:11:48,310
Thank goodness.

148
00:11:49,010 --> 00:11:51,980
Since this one has the mole,
she must be my Seo Rin.

149
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:54,820
- Sir.
- Yes?

150
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:57,820
She needs emergency surgery.
First, I need you to sign here.

151
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,390
Sign?

152
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:01,860
Here you go.

153
00:12:07,430 --> 00:12:08,430
Hey...

154
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:11,940
What's going to happen to Jang Mi?

155
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:18,740
Nurse.

156
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:22,150
- Yes?
- Move my Seo Rin to the VIP suite.

157
00:12:22,450 --> 00:12:25,350
- Right now.
- Yes, ma'am. I'll get it ready.

158
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,820
What?

159
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:30,820
Director Ma was in a car accident?

160
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,620
My mom just told me.

161
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:35,090
How is she?

162
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:37,560
(Surgery in Progress)

163
00:12:40,330 --> 00:12:41,570
What happened?

164
00:12:41,570 --> 00:12:43,170
What happened to Jang Mi?

165
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:45,140
Baek Ho.

166
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:49,010
Why do these things keep happening
to our family?

167
00:12:51,110 --> 00:12:52,180
I'm losing my mind.

168
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,610
(Operating Room)

169
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:57,750
Is it really bad?

170
00:13:03,650 --> 00:13:04,660
Jang Mi.

171
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:12,560
What?

172
00:13:13,130 --> 00:13:14,930
Who got in a car accident?

173
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:17,000
Oh Jang Mi.

174
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:22,770
Baek Ho got a call from her brother,
and he just ran out, pale as a ghost.

175
00:13:23,070 --> 00:13:24,780
Is she badly hurt?

176
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,210
It sounds like it's really serious.

177
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:33,620
Goodness, how can so many terrible things
keep happening to that family?

178
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:37,720
I know I shouldn't say this,

179
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:42,330
but I'm scared her bad luck
might rub off on our Baek Ho.

180
00:13:42,460 --> 00:13:45,760
What are you talking about?
You're a lawyer. How can you think that?

181
00:13:45,830 --> 00:13:47,600
That's them, this is us.

182
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,200
Anyway,

183
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:52,870
I just hope the poor girl
will be all right.

184
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:56,940
- Right.
- Imagine how devastated Baek Ho must be.

185
00:13:57,310 --> 00:14:00,110
If something happens to her...

186
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:03,410
Hey, don't even say that.
It's horrible to even think about.

187
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:06,050
Honey, I'm sorry.

188
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:09,750
You must still have trauma
from the accident.

189
00:14:26,770 --> 00:14:27,810
Seo Rin.

190
00:14:29,010 --> 00:14:30,170
You can't go yet.

191
00:14:31,780 --> 00:14:33,540
I still need you.

192
00:14:34,710 --> 00:14:36,050
Open your eyes, Ma Seo Rin.

193
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:37,820
Wake up.

194
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:39,820
I said, get up!

195
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:48,090
There's no way...

196
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:50,860
Chairman Ma, that old fool,
will give me Dream Group.

197
00:14:51,730 --> 00:14:53,200
I need Seo Rin for that.

198
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:55,470
Not yet, Seo Rin.

199
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:59,300
For 30 years, my entire youth...

200
00:14:59,970 --> 00:15:01,940
has been spent chasing my one dream.

201
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:05,010
Open your eyes.

202
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:27,100
Who is that? She looks just like me.

203
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:29,870
What's going on?

204
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:31,970
Am I dead?

205
00:15:34,070 --> 00:15:35,340
Did I just leave my own body?

206
00:15:36,210 --> 00:15:37,570
Who did this to me?

207
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:40,110
By the way...

208
00:15:41,110 --> 00:15:43,210
Who was I?

209
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:54,460
Who is he?

210
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:07,840
You people...

211
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,670
Who are you?

212
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:11,180
Seo Rin, open your eyes.

213
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:12,640
No!

214
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:13,740
Ma Seo Rin!

215
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,390
Seo Rin, open your eyes.

216
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,560
Seo Rin, please open your eyes.

217
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,760
Come on, wake up.

218
00:16:29,290 --> 00:16:31,830
Seo Rin, can you hear your mother?

219
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:33,800
Please open your eyes.

220
00:16:37,770 --> 00:16:38,940
Seo Rin.

221
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:39,970
My dear girl.

222
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:42,040
What on earth happened?

223
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:46,740
Where was she going?
Why was she in a car accident?

224
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,550
I'm so sorry, Father.

225
00:16:53,650 --> 00:16:55,450
Wait, Seo Rin.

226
00:16:55,450 --> 00:16:56,590
Are you coming to?

227
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:59,660
It's me, It's Mom.
Seo Rin, do you recognize me?

228
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:01,490
Seo Rin, it's Grandpa.

229
00:17:01,890 --> 00:17:05,260
My sweet girl, what happened to you?

230
00:17:07,130 --> 00:17:08,130
Mom?

231
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:11,900
(Surgery in Progress)

232
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,500
When did she go into surgery?

233
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:15,540
Is Jang Mi badly hurt?

234
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:17,510
How bad is it?

235
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:19,340
It's serious.

236
00:17:19,910 --> 00:17:20,910
No.

237
00:17:21,810 --> 00:17:23,510
It hasn't been that long since Dad died.

238
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:25,250
Why does this keep happening?

239
00:17:30,850 --> 00:17:31,860
(Surgery in Progress)

240
00:17:36,490 --> 00:17:39,130
Excuse me, Doctor.
The surgery went well, right?

241
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:41,800
- Jang Mi's going to be okay, right?
- How is she?

242
00:17:41,870 --> 00:17:44,200
- She's okay now, right?
- We've stopped the bleeding.

243
00:17:44,270 --> 00:17:45,770
- Thank you.
- However...

244
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:48,410
Due to the severe impact
to her head during the accident,

245
00:17:48,410 --> 00:17:50,270
she sustained temporary brain damage,

246
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:53,940
which has left her
in an unconscious state.

247
00:17:54,450 --> 00:17:56,680
In other words, she's in a coma.

248
00:17:58,150 --> 00:18:01,290
- What?
- We'll move her to the ICU...

249
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:02,850
and monitor her progress for 24 hours.

250
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:05,260
No.

251
00:18:06,190 --> 00:18:08,090
(Operating Room)

252
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:23,070
Jang Mi, no.

253
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,610
How could this happen...

254
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,750
Seo Rin, it's Mom.

255
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:36,090
Do you recognize me?

256
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:43,490
Thank goodness.
You're awake. That's all that matters.

257
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:47,660
Seo Rin, you're okay now.

258
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:50,030
Everything's going to be okay, all right?

259
00:18:54,810 --> 00:18:56,710
- Check her vitals.
- Yes, Doctor.

260
00:18:56,710 --> 00:18:57,710
What's her BP?

261
00:18:58,140 --> 00:19:01,410
- It's normal.
- Ms. Ma, this might be a bit bright.

262
00:19:02,850 --> 00:19:03,910
Can you hear me?

263
00:19:04,850 --> 00:19:06,450
Where am I?

264
00:19:09,190 --> 00:19:10,590
Who are all of you?

265
00:19:14,930 --> 00:19:17,560
I don't know anything.

266
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:20,160
What's wrong with her?

267
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:22,570
- Ma Seo Rin.
- Seo Rin.

268
00:19:22,930 --> 00:19:26,200
What do you mean you don't know anything?

269
00:19:26,700 --> 00:19:29,670
You don't even know you're Seo Rin?

270
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:34,810
I don't know who I am...

271
00:19:34,810 --> 00:19:36,050
Seo Rin.

272
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:40,380
Hey, Dr. Kim.
What's wrong with my granddaughter?

273
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:47,020
Due to the shock from the accident,

274
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:49,890
the patient has temporary amnesia.

275
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:51,300
Amnesia?

276
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:52,960
So...

277
00:19:53,430 --> 00:19:56,030
you're sure it's temporary, right?

278
00:19:58,770 --> 00:19:59,770
Yes.

279
00:20:04,710 --> 00:20:07,180
It's a classic case
of psychogenic amnesia.

280
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:11,920
The shock from the accident has triggered
a psychological defense mechanism,

281
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:15,290
which has temporarily blocked
parts of her memory.

282
00:20:15,850 --> 00:20:19,290
She may not recognize her own name
or even the people around her,

283
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:22,690
but depending on her family's care,
she could improve quickly,

284
00:20:23,090 --> 00:20:24,490
or her condition could worsen.

285
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:27,900
If you provide a stable,
stress-free environment,

286
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:31,640
her memories will gradually come back.
Please, try not to worry.

287
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:35,610
What about the scumbag
who hit our Seo Rin?

288
00:20:36,610 --> 00:20:39,380
It was a hit-and-run,
but the police will catch the driver.

289
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,710
Tell the police to make sure
they catch the driver.

290
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:41,750
No.

291
00:20:42,550 --> 00:20:44,310
Tell them they'd better catch the driver.

292
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:47,750
Or else I'll go after the cops themselves.

293
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:50,220
Yes. Of course the driver
has to be caught.

294
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,900
Can't you do your job properly?

295
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:11,480
What would you have done
if something had happened to my Seo Rin?

296
00:21:11,540 --> 00:21:13,410
- I'm sorry.
- I'm sick of your apologies.

297
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:18,580
Tell your guy to lay low and stay hidden.

298
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:21,250
If he gets caught by the police,

299
00:21:22,420 --> 00:21:24,090
all the work we've been doing
for the past 30 years...

300
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:25,820
will be wasted. Got it?

301
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:28,030
Yes.

302
00:21:30,530 --> 00:21:31,630
Chairman Ma...

303
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:34,230
will stop at nothing to catch him.

304
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,500
If...

305
00:21:38,140 --> 00:21:39,840
it gets out that I'm behind this,

306
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:42,010
we're all...

307
00:21:43,010 --> 00:21:44,470
finished.

308
00:22:16,610 --> 00:22:17,640
Jang Mi.

309
00:22:18,710 --> 00:22:19,840
Wake up.

310
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:22,710
You can't just lie here like this.

311
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,450
Please.

312
00:22:26,980 --> 00:22:28,420
Please, just wake up.

313
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:35,160
(Intensive Care Unit)

314
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:50,570
How are you feeling today?

315
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,440
Excuse me.

316
00:22:54,540 --> 00:22:55,850
Who am I?

317
00:22:56,510 --> 00:22:58,050
And why am I here?

318
00:22:58,950 --> 00:23:01,720
Why can't I remember a thing?

319
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:04,990
Don't try to force it.

320
00:23:05,190 --> 00:23:07,590
You need to rest for now.

321
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:10,130
I don't remember anything at all.

322
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:13,500
Who am I?

323
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:14,530
Tell me, please.

324
00:23:15,570 --> 00:23:16,630
What did you say?

325
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:20,170
Seo Rin has amnesia?

326
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:23,410
Oh my goodness. How could this happen?

327
00:23:24,210 --> 00:23:28,680
- Oh, no.
- Father, what happened to Director Ma?

328
00:23:29,980 --> 00:23:31,080
I just feel so bad.

329
00:23:31,550 --> 00:23:33,450
Did they catch the person
who hit Director Ma?

330
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:35,120
Not yet.

331
00:23:35,890 --> 00:23:37,120
Just let me get my hands on whoever it is.

332
00:23:37,650 --> 00:23:38,890
How dare they hit my granddaughter...

333
00:23:38,990 --> 00:23:41,460
She's the granddaughter
of the Chairman of Dream Group.

334
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:43,660
How dare they put her in that condition?

335
00:23:45,360 --> 00:23:49,430
Honey, what's going to happen to Seo Rin?

336
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:53,770
Will her memory never come back?

337
00:23:53,770 --> 00:23:54,940
Don't be ridiculous.

338
00:23:57,140 --> 00:23:59,540
You seem to be hoping for that, San Wol,

339
00:23:59,540 --> 00:24:01,610
but once my Seo Rin gets some rest,

340
00:24:02,110 --> 00:24:04,050
everything will go back to normal soon.

341
00:24:05,080 --> 00:24:06,520
So don't get your hopes up.

342
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:09,850
Oh my goodness.
What a horrible thing to say!

343
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:13,760
I'm worried sick, not happy!
If I were, I'd be doomed!

344
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:15,730
Why did you come here
instead of looking after her?

345
00:24:15,990 --> 00:24:17,630
They said she can go home tomorrow,

346
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:20,860
so I just came home to get her clothes
and her belongings.

347
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,400
She's being discharged already?

348
00:24:23,470 --> 00:24:25,770
That's right. Are you disappointed?

349
00:24:25,840 --> 00:24:28,310
Of course not, ma'am.
Why would I be disappointed?

350
00:24:28,770 --> 00:24:31,270
I was genuinely worried about her.

351
00:24:31,910 --> 00:24:33,440
We're all family now, after all.

352
00:24:39,820 --> 00:24:43,950
I don't know why she's so twisted.
She just has such a nasty attitude.

353
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,030
Jang Mi, do you remember?

354
00:24:53,300 --> 00:24:54,970
The day we first met.

355
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:58,900
- Are you going to let go or not?
- I'm not letting go.

356
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:03,840
- Goodness, thanks a lot.
- Oh, my.

357
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:11,880
You were so stubborn,
just shoving me aside...

358
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:15,350
and yelling at me.
Where did that spitfire go?

359
00:25:16,320 --> 00:25:17,690
Lying here like this...

360
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:19,960
is not like you at all, Jang Mi.

361
00:25:21,860 --> 00:25:23,690
I made a vow to your father.

362
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:28,400
I promised I'd always
cherish and protect you.

363
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:32,970
But how can I do that
if you just keep lying here?

364
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:36,440
I'll be too ashamed to ever face him.

365
00:25:42,810 --> 00:25:45,950
Just wake up for me, Jang Mi.

366
00:25:48,250 --> 00:25:49,520
You don't have to say a word.

367
00:25:50,950 --> 00:25:52,490
It's okay if you don't even know who I am.

368
00:25:53,490 --> 00:25:55,690
Just wake up alive,

369
00:25:57,630 --> 00:25:59,160
and leave the rest to me.

370
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,200
Never again...

371
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,870
will I lose you, Jang Mi.

372
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,520
What's with the roses?

373
00:26:24,290 --> 00:26:25,390
Roses? Wait, Jang Mi?

374
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,670
Thank you. Let's go.

375
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,180
(Patient: Ma Seo Rin)

376
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:51,380
That's my Jang Mi.

377
00:26:52,150 --> 00:26:54,880
My daughter Jang Mi is so pretty!

378
00:26:55,520 --> 00:26:57,550
- Jang Mi is pretty.
- Jang Mi.

379
00:26:57,650 --> 00:26:58,920
- Jang Mi.
- Jang Mi.

380
00:26:58,990 --> 00:27:00,020
- Jang Mi.
- Oh Jang Mi.

381
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:02,730
- Jang Mi.
- Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

382
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,290
- Jang Mi.
- Jang Mi is pretty.

383
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:05,400
- You're my daughter.
- Oh Jang Mi.

384
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:07,430
- Whatever they say, you're my daughter!
- Oh Jang Mi.

385
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:08,500
Jang Mi.

386
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:13,300
No.

387
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:17,710
(Name: Ma Seo Rin)

388
00:27:19,910 --> 00:27:21,010
"Ma Seo Rin?"

389
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:29,550
Ma Seo Rin!

390
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:47,540
Ma Seo Rin!

391
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,050
Seo Rin.

392
00:28:01,050 --> 00:28:02,050
Ma Seo Rin.

393
00:28:02,420 --> 00:28:03,850
What happened to Seo Rin?

394
00:28:06,290 --> 00:28:07,290
Seo Rin!

395
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:09,530
Ma Seo Rin!

396
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:26,810
(The First Man)

397
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:31,480
If I was admitted as Ma Seo Rin,
then Seo Rin must be here as Oh Jang Mi.

398
00:28:31,950 --> 00:28:32,980
Seo Rin...

399
00:28:33,550 --> 00:28:34,750
Oh no.

400
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:37,190
There was an accident that day.

401
00:28:37,220 --> 00:28:39,520
Has this person ever been here?

402
00:28:39,820 --> 00:28:41,490
I hope both of them are okay.

403
00:28:41,790 --> 00:28:42,990
Both of them?

404
00:28:42,990 --> 00:28:45,500
Seo Rin, I'm borrowing your identity.

405
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:48,800
Just you wait, Chae Hwa Young!

406
00:28:48,800 --> 00:28:49,930
I'm going to make your life
a living nightmare.

407
00:28:51,870 --> 00:28:53,870
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
